Package: noisecanceling
Title: Psychometric analysis of likert scales: methods for controlling for acquiescence bias
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Primi", "Ricardo", , "rprimi@mac.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4227-6745"))
Description: This package implements classical and modern (IRT) psychometric analyses that control for acquiescence bias. The package wraps a number of functions of the Psych package in order to facilitate the analysis of multidimensional scales .
